title: [Emerald Forest, Secluded Path]
description: Majestic oak trees arch high overhead, forming a corridor of crooked branches and rustling breezes.  A pair of dragonflies chase one another in an expanding spiral through hazy shafts of sunlight.  A faint path of amber leaves and loamy earth wanders aimlessly through the middle.

Majestic oak trees arch high overhead, forming a corridor of crooked branches and rustling breezes.  A pair of luna moths chase one another in an expanding spiral through silver shafts of moonlight.  A faint path of amber leaves and loamy earth wanders aimlessly through the middle.
